31:23.800 --> 31:25.093
What?

31:25.176 --> 31:27.137
Did Shay stay home
to take this job

31:27.178 --> 31:29.681
to conduct
her own investigation?

31:29.723 --> 31:30.807
No.

31:30.849 --> 31:32.308
We need the money.

31:33.268 --> 31:35.812
You are so lying, Shay.

31:35.854 --> 31:38.440
