31:45.196 --> 31:46.614
Look, everything's fine.

31:48.700 --> 31:51.536
-Mostly.
-Mostly?

31:52.454 --> 31:54.205
It's just...

31:54.289 --> 31:56.666
the little girl, Blair, she...

31:58.084 --> 31:59.878
