something in a creepy house,

32:12.349 --> 32:16.728
you take that shit seriously
100% of the time.

32:16.770 --> 32:20.065
And you would be the
world's most trash babysitter.

32:23.193 --> 32:24.444
I saw that look.

32:24.527 --> 32:27.072
