35:58.783 --> 36:00.243
Is that you?

36:00.285 --> 36:02.370
Hey, Chase.

36:02.454 --> 36:04.581
Your mom went to the hospital.

36:04.622 --> 36:05.999
Who are you?

36:06.082 --> 36:08.001
It's... Shay.

36:08.084 --> 36:09.127
Stay back.

36:09.210 --> 36:11.046
It's okay.

36:11.129 --> 36:13.298
It's okay. It's me. Remember?

36:13.340 --> 36:14.674
We met earlier.

36:14.758 --> 36:16.468
I'm just here
to keep an eye on you guys

36:16.509 --> 36:18.011
