42:35.388 --> 42:38.099
Oh.

42:38.892 --> 42:41.603
Thought I saw something outside.

42:50.612 --> 42:52.906
What is it?

42:58.286 --> 43:00.413
Where'd it go?

43:04.501 --> 43:05.877
I want my mom.

43:34.572 --> 43:38.410
It's so meant to be.

43:38.451 --> 43:40.412
Oh, my God.

43:43.331 --> 43:45.250
I'm on my way, my queen.

43:52.757 --> 43:55.635
