53:30.168 --> 53:31.419
I can't hear you.

53:31.503 --> 53:33.004
Shay!

53:33.046 --> 53:36.174
Tell them Hopkins, Mangham.

53:36.257 --> 53:38.510
Jas? Shit, Jas, shit.

